sketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In front of the watching President Emmanuel Macron, France kept battling, closing the gap to 65-59 on Evan Fournier's three-pointer late in the third quarter, only for James to respond in kind and take his own tally into double figures.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9992142622788484, \"rank\": 0.0007806452585041724, \"text\": \"President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9922036354502598, \"rank\": 0.007857624972537051, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evan Fournier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Fournier\"}, {\"begin\": 2207, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.13892547217619e-20, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France refused to go away in a tense fourth quarter, and eight unanswered points cut the deficit to 82-79 on a basket from Wembanyama with less than three minutes on the clock.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9922036354502598, \"rank\": 0.007857624972537051, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But France had no answer as Curry sank three three-pointers inside the final two minutes to take the game away from them.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2459, \"end\": 2465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9922036354502598, \"rank\": 0.007857624972537051, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the 2024 Olympic Games with 14 hours of televised action on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player each day.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"tex